ttps:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-2fi","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":26443,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/21\/iman-haya-speaking-less\/","url_meta":{"origin":8636,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Modesty, speaking less are branches of faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cModesty and reticence are two branches of faith. Profanity and temerity are two branches of hypocrisy.\u201d Imam al-Tirmidhi commented, \u201cReticence is to speak little. Profanity is to speak obscenely. Temerity is to speak too often, such as those\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8630,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/22\/poetry-shir-entire-tribe\/","url_meta":{"origin":8636,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Satire: Worst liar attacks entire tribe in poetry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the greatest liar among people is a man who insults another man by satirizing the entire tribe, and a man who disowns his father and accuses his mother of adultery.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3761 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32141,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/